          "activities": [
            {
              "text": "Teruel is Spain's capital of DOP ham. The province produces high-altitude serrano ham raised in the sierras, cured for a minimum of 14 months. Bars on Plaza del Torico serve it in thin slices accompanied by a glass of local wine.",
