              "text": "Late afternoon swim at one of Costa Teguise's beaches, Lanzarote's most family-friendly northern resort. Or head up to Haría and the Valley of a Thousand Palms—a green oasis in the northern hills, accessible in 20 minutes from Costa Teguise.",
