          "activities": [
            {
              "text": "Guided hike into the caldera from Los Brecitos: several operators offer accompanied descents in small groups, with a 4x4 bus to reach the starting point from Los Llanos de Aridane. It's the recommended option if you don't know the trail, as ravines can be slippery and weather changes fast inside.",
