            },
            {
              "text": "The Basilica of Santa María la Mayor displays its Gothic portals—the Portal of the Apostles and the Portal of the Virgins—carved in the 14th and 15th centuries. The spiral staircase of the choir loft is entirely covered with painted reliefs.",
              "place_id": "",
              "visit_duration_min": 75
