          "activities": [
            {
              "text": "The Ebro canyon (Hoces del Alto Ebro y Rudrón) offers spectacular hikes from Orbaneja. The circular route linking Orbaneja del Castillo to Valdelateja follows the canyon for 17 km—allow a good half-day. If you prefer something shorter, the GR-99 between Pesquera de Ebro and Manzanedo offers the best gorge views in 2-3 hours.",
