              "text": "Mérida's cuisine is that of the dehesa—the oak-pasture landscape covering much of Extremadura. Try Iberian pork in all its forms (lomo, presa, secreto), caldereta de cordero (lamb stew), and wines from Tierra de Barros, the wine zone extending south toward Almendralejo.",
              "place_id": "",
              "activity_duration_min": 90,
