              "text": "Sunset walk along Paseo del Salón or higher up, around the Fuencisla sanctuary—Segovia's patron saint. The view of the Alcázar ablaze with slanting sun is the image you'll remember. In winter, the old town's façades are illuminated and the aqueduct becomes even more dramatic. Locals take their evening paseo here: Segovians are so accustomed to their city they forget it while loving it.",
