              "text": "On the road from Salamanca, recommended stop at Toro—30 km detour via N-122. PDO Toro vineyards and the Romanesque-Byzantine Collegiate Church of Santa María la Mayor from the 12th century, with golden octagonal façade. If time is tight, go straight to Zamora. Otherwise, quick tasting at Bodegas Liberalia or Estancia Piedra is enough to understand why Toro wines have been rising for 20 years: tannic tinta de toro, lots of structure, perfect with Castilian meats.",
