          ],
          "activities": [
            {
              "text": "Walk along the Segre at sunset. The river cuts through the city and the banks have been developed—bike paths, picnic areas, even kayak and canoe launches. From here you get the finest view of the Seu Vella lit up after nightfall. Locals come for their evening jog, giving a strangely provincial feel to a city of 140,000. Sample caracoles a la llauna or xató at an old-town tavern to finish.",
