            {
              "text": "Sunday's market, on Plaça Sant Joan and all around, is one of inland Catalonia's most authentic. Urgell producers, Pyrenean cheeses, arbequina oil, mountain honey, coca de recapte (Catalan topped flatbread). It's also a chance to hear western Catalan, slightly different from Barcelona's. Starts early—by 9 AM it's already packed.",
