          "activities": [
            {
              "text": "The Parc Olímpic del Segre, created for the canoe-kayak events of the 1992 Barcelona Olympics, still offers rafting and kayaking on whitewater on the artificial canal and natural river. World championships have been held here several times. Good option for an afternoon of adrenaline if you prefer to save the Noguera Pallaresa, wilder, for tomorrow. Morning or afternoon sessions, from €35 per descent.",
