          "activities": [
            {
              "text": "The grand classic: rafting descent from Llavorsí to Sort, 18 km, the most intense stretch of the Noguera Pallaresa. On the program: legendary rapids La Rentadora (the \"washing machine\"), La Sirga, Quatre Llarg, and—if flow permits—jump off the Sort dam. Level class III-IV, accessible to beginners in good shape. The full descent takes 1.5 to 2 hours. Several operators depart from the base at Llavorsí or directly from Sort.",
              "place_id": "",
              "activity_duration_min": 180,
