            {
              "text": "For those who prefer to keep their feet (almost) dry: canyoning in the Barranc de Sant Pere or hydrospeed descent (whitewater swimming on a board). Children from age 4 can do mini-rafting on the Baró-Figueretes section, calmer. Sort's entire ecosystem revolves around water, and it has obvious educational virtues for family travel.",
