              "text": "The City of Arts and Sciences impresses by its sheer scale—the complex designed by Calatrava and Bofill stretches two kilometers along the old Turia riverbed. The Hemisfèric and Museu de les Ciències merit the entrance fee; the Oceanogràfic, Europe's largest aquarium according to its official site, deserves an entire half-day.",
