          "visits": [
            {
              "text": "Valencia's central market is perhaps Spain's most beautiful covered market—an Art Deco nave of iron and ceramic inaugurated in 1928 that still houses over 900 stalls today. Come between 9am and 11am to see it in action. After 1pm, half the stalls close.",
